      <abstract>
        <p>Correction: brief report on June 15 about second-quarter profit of Bear Stearns Companies misstated a charge taken</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A brief report by Bloomberg News in Business Day yesterday about the second-quarter profit of the Bear Stearns Companies misstated the amount of a charge taken in connection with a federal court judgment against the firm. The charge was 63 cents a share, not 66 cents.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>A brief report by Bloomberg News in Business Day yesterday about the second-quarter profit of the Bear Stearns Companies misstated the amount of a charge taken in connection with a federal court judgment against the firm. The charge was 63 cents a share, not 66 cents.</p>
